对了，我说出了一些对方没想到的事情，对人家也有好处，这有什么问题呢？ 我是个纯理科生，说话太直是我的不对，所以我现在在改，我希望我能够用让人舒服的方式，给我的朋友提意见，我提意见，也许我能帮到对方，也许不能。但我不提，我永远只能眼睁睁看对方如小白鼠一样测验我心中的想法。 我不愿我提意见对方讨厌我，但我更不愿为了不让对方讨厌就眼睁睁的看对方走错路！（我再说一遍我是提意见，我不是说不提对方一定走错路！而是万一我的意见能避免对方走错路！ 所以我来知乎提问，如何正确地提意见"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-48d1d8498e1bcdd4154acea79ff62e9a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "79 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/40288998"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0I9vWEyoXpyKojEAMaBzgzMjI5MDAg6MjxtQUwCDjoDUAmcgg0MDI4ODk5OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1620414417.1928768", "card_id": "Q_456002749", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 432}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "努力会失败，不努力也会失败，人为什么还要努力？努力的意义是啥？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-6458416dc52a2ffa5e467a9f0321f48e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/456002749"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9vWEyoXpyKojEAMaCDYzNjEzOTU0ILu1hYQGMAM4pwRAJ3IJNDU2MDAyNzQ5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1620414417.1931336", "card_id": "Q_378449678", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 50}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "被病娇喜欢是一种什么感觉？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-5225cb2274f5d7d53efa026b791ff1e5_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/378449678"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9vWEyoXpyKojEAMaCDQ2Mzc4Mzk5IOGQoPMFMAE4/QJAKHIJMzc4NDQ5Njc4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1620414417.1933763", "card_id": "Q_425556684",